					<p>Throughout history, new gadgets and services have completely disrupted entire industries. Yet when these technologies were invented, many people doubted they would amount to much more than rumors or brief fads.</p><p>Even the brightest names in business and technology are no exception to such skepticism and short-sightedness. From the proliferation of the post office to the debut of the smartphone, pioneers and intellectuals in the tech field have often underestimated the potential of new ideas to transform society. </p><p>Check out the video above to hear Entrepreneur Network partner Patrick Bet-David share some of the most off-the-mark predictions of all time.</p><p><em>Watch more YouTube videos from <a>Bet-David on his channel.</a></em></p><p></p><p><a><em>Entrepreneur Network</em></a> <em>is a </em><a><em>premium video network</em></a><em> providing entertainment, education and inspiration from successful entrepreneurs and thought leaders. We provide expertise and opportunities to accelerate brand growth and effectively monetize video and audio content distributed across all digital platforms for the business genre.</em></p><p><em>EN is partnered with hundreds of top </em><a><em>YouTube channels</em></a><em> in the business vertical and provides partners with distribution on </em><a><em>Entrepreneur.com</em></a><em> as well as our apps on </em><a><em>Amazon Fire</em></a><em>, </em><a><em>Roku</em></a><em> and </em><a><em>Apple TV</em></a><em>.</em></p><p></p>				
				
